## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="571a8-314">El <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> codifica un búfer de caracteres a la vez, en lugar de carácter a carácter.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-314">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> encodes a buffer of characters all at once, rather than character by character.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="571a8-315">Se produce una excepción cuando el <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Flush%2A> método se llama si se encuentran los errores de codificación.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-315">An exception is thrown when the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Flush%2A> method is called if any encoding errors are encountered.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="571a8-316">El <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> propiedad solo se aplica a la <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instancias que se crean con los valores especificados <xref:System.IO.Stream> o con el nombre de archivo especificado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-316">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property only applies to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances that are created either with the specified <xref:System.IO.Stream> or with the specified file name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="571a8-317">Si el <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instancia se crea con los valores especificados <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>, <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> reemplaza a la codificación de subyacente <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-317">If the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance is created with the specified <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property is overridden by the encoding of the underlying <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="571a8-318">Por ejemplo, si esta propiedad se establece en Unicode (UTF-16) para un determinado <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>, pero el escritor subyacente es un <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> (que se deriva de <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>) con la codificación establecida en UTF8, la salida será con codificación UTF-8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-318">For example, if this property is set to Unicode (UTF-16) for a particular <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>, but the underlying writer is a <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> (which derives from <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>) with its encoding set to UTF8, the output will be UTF-8 encoded.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="571a8-319">Si el <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instancia se crea con otros parámetros de salida, el <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> propiedad se omite.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-319">If the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance is created with other output parameters, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property is ignored.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="571a8-320">En el ejemplo siguiente:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-320">In the following example:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="571a8-321">El valor predeterminado de <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> es `Encoding.UTF8`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-321">The default value of <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> is `Encoding.UTF8`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="571a8-322">El <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> está establecido en `Encoding.Unicode` y <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>invalidaciones de codificación de la <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> configuración.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-322">The <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> is set to `Encoding.Unicode` and the <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>’s encoding overrides the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> setting.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="571a8-323">El resultado será `Encoding.Unicode`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-323">The output will be `Encoding.Unicode`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using (StreamWriter output =  
    new StreamWriter(new FileStream("Xml01.xml", FileMode.Create), Encoding.Unicode))  
{  
    using (XmlWriter xmlWriter =  
        XmlWriter.Create(output, new XmlWriterSettings()))  
    {  
        xmlWriter.WriteStartDocument();  
        xmlWriter.WriteStartElement("Root");  
        xmlWriter.WriteEndElement();  
        xmlWriter.WriteEndDocument();  
    }  
}  
```  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="571a8-324">No aceptan un <xref:System.Text.Encoding> objeto desde un origen de confianza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="571a8-324">Do not accept an <xref:System.Text.Encoding> object from an untrusted source.</span></span>  
  
   
  
